01:12:01.340 --> 01:12:03.830
I mean, it could very well
be that in your computer

01:12:03.830 --> 01:12:07.470
that there is one piece of
software that is compute--

01:12:07.470 --> 01:12:10.860
you know, communicating to the
central server somewhere in the sky

01:12:10.860 --> 01:12:14.630
and telling them that you are,
