01:21:08.390 --> 01:21:09.690
of the day looking at the facts.

01:21:09.690 --> 01:21:11.290
But I think they both
have that same basic--

01:21:11.290 --> 01:21:14.430
&gt;&gt; John Bergmayer: So I think to
