01:21:19.580 --> 01:21:23.280
that I don't really own because
I'm just borrowing something

01:21:23.280 --> 01:21:27.890
and that's fine and that's
not unique to software.

01:21:27.890 --> 01:21:29.190
&gt;&gt; Erik Bertin: All right.

